OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,FBecause he did not hit his wife, Pete
OL,7,Fdid not see his behaviour for what it
OL,8,Fwas - abuse.
OL,10,FNow though, that has changed.
OL,12,FThrough domestic abuse charity
OL,13,FFearFree, Pete has received support to
OL,14,Fchange his behaviour.
OL,16,FFor the first time, he says he can
OL,17,F"sleep peacefully" knowing he is no
OL,18,Flonger an abusive husband.
