OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,FSpeaking anonymously to ITV News for
OL,7,Fthe protection of his family, Pete
OL,8,Fsaid: "I was shouting a lot, slamming
OL,9,Fthings, stamping things around the
OL,10,Fhouse, anything like that.
OL,12,F"I could see that my wife was on
OL,13,Feggshells. I don't even know why I was
OL,14,Fdoing that."
OL,16,FOne day Pete said Alison sat him down
OL,17,Fand challenged his behaviour.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@LO]
