OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,F"My wife said 'can't you see the way
OL,7,Fyour behaviour is, the way you are
OL,8,Ftalking to me... it's not right'," he
OL,9,Freflected.
OL,11,FHe went to his doctor to ask for help
OL,12,Fand was given a support worker, who
OL,13,Fsigned him up to the 25-week course
OL,14,Fwith FearFree.
OL,16,F"The word abuse, to me, meant that the
OL,17,Fperson hit their partner - but I never
OL,18,Fhit my wife. I was verbally abusive.
