OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,F"I didn't find that out until it was
OL,7,Fpointed out a bit by my wife, but then
OL,8,FI went on the course and then I
OL,9,Frealised 'I am verbally abusive, yeah,
OL,10,Fmy attitude is not right at all'."
OL,12,FThe course, run across
OL,13,FGloucestershire, Wiltshire and Devon,
OL,14,Fsupports people in changing their
OL,15,Fbehaviour and encourages healthy
OL,16,Frelationships.
