OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,FPete said: "I didn't like the idea of
OL,7,Fbeing in a group with say five men..
OL,8,Fmy father always said 'big boys don't
OL,9,Fcry, you don't show your feelings' and
OL,10,Fthat's what it was with the group."
OL,12,FAfter completing the course, Pete
OL,13,Fasked organisers if he could do it all
OL,14,Fover again as he feared he hadn't
OL,15,Factually learnt from it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
