OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,F"Blokes out there might judge me, they
OL,7,Fcan judge me as much as they want -
OL,8,FI'm not bothered because I'm able to
OL,9,Fput my head on my pillow at night now
OL,10,Fnext to my wife and sleep peacefully
OL,11,Fwithout any arguments."
OL,13,FAlison told ITV News their
OL,14,Frelationship is "massively different
OL,15,Fnow".
OL,17,FShe said: "It felt as if I didn't have
OL,18,Fa voice, I wasn't really allowed an
OL,19,Fopinion. I wasn't sure why he was
OL,20,Fdoing those things.
