OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,F"(Our relationship is) massively
OL,7,Fdifferent now. We can discuss whatever
OL,8,Fis going on in our lives. I don't feel
OL,9,Fnervous, I don't feel like I'm walking
OL,10,Fon eggshells.
OL,12,F"It's much calmer and I feel as if I
OL,13,Fhave a voice now and I'm not afraid to
OL,14,Fsay when I have a problem. This course
OL,15,Fdefinitely does work."
OL,17,FGemma Vinton, Head of Service at
OL,18,FFearFree, said of the course: "People
OL,19,Fare offered a 25 week programme, often
OL,20,Fa group programme.
