OL,3,C'I used to abuse my wife - this is how
OL,4,CI changed my ways'
OL,6,F"That programme really is a psycho-
OL,7,Feducation, really detailed package
OL,8,Fthat unpicks the reasons that person
OL,9,Fis demonstrating abusive behaviour and
OL,10,Fgives people coping strategies to look
OL,11,Fat what alternatives might be."
OL,13,FShe added: "People will ask, does it
OL,14,Falways work?
OL,16,F"The honest answer is nothing always
OL,17,Fworks, but if we have someone who
OL,18,Freally wants to work with us and wants
OL,19,Fto change, we find these sessions
OL,20,Fincredibly helpful.
